These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, sprite, water
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, french, indian, nigerian
1. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
2. the nigerian is on the left or right of the brazilian##3
3. the brazilian is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking water is somewhere to the left of the nigerian##5
5. the brazilian is the person drinking lemonade##1
6. the person drinking sprite is the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Beverage      | water  | hot-chocolate | lemonade  | sprite |
| Nationality   | indian | nigerian      | brazilian | french |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, egyptian, italian, malaysian
4 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, goat, horse
1. the egyptian is between the owner of the bird and the owner of the horse##2
2. the malaysian is somewhere to the left of the owner of the horse##5
3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
4. the owner of the bird is on the right of the malaysian##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Nationality   | malaysian | italian | egyptian   | australian |
| Pet           | goat      | bird    | chinchilla | horse      |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, corn, peach, potato
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, car, quad-bike, train
1. the person eating corn is the person driving the car##1
2. the person driving the train is on the right of the person eating corn##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bus##5
4. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the person eating peach##3
5. the person eating potato is somewhere to the right of the person driving the train##5
6. the person eating corn is somewhere to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | corn | cabbage | peach     | potato |
| Transport   | car  | train   | quad-bike | bus    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, singing, skydiving, woodworking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, epic, family, romance
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the right of the person watching family movies##5
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person watching romance movies and the person watching epic movies##2
4. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3
5. the person watching romance movies is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | skydiving | card-games | singing | woodworking |
| Movie-Genre   | romance   | family     | epic    | crime       |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-5::.
There 4 different types of food: banana, corn, eggplant, kale
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, western, zombie
1. the person eating kale is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5
2. the person eating kale is on the left or right of the person eating eggplant##3
3. the person eating eggplant is somewhere to the left of the person eating banana##5
4. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
5. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the person eating corn##3
6. the person eating kale is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3     |    4    |
| Food          | eggplant | kale   | banana   | corn    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery  | zombie | disaster | western |

