The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, librarian, mechanic, scientist
1. the librarian is on the right of the scientist##1
2. the person eating strawberry is somewhere to the left of the mechanic##5
3. the person eating strawberry is on the left or right of the person eating pear##3
4. the person eating mango is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
5. the mechanic is somewhere to the left of the designer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Food   | mango     | strawberry | pear     | carrot   |
| Job    | scientist | librarian  | mechanic | designer |

