.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, iced-tea, milk
There 4 different types of food: lemon, pear, potato, tomato
1. the person eating potato is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the person eating tomato##5
5. the person eating pear is somewhere to the right of the person eating lemon##5
6. the person eating lemon is somewhere to the left of the person eating potato##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |  4   |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | iced-tea | milk   | cola |
| Food       | lemon       | potato   | tomato | pear |

