.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, mirinda, tea
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, surfing, water-polo, weightlifting
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
2. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##5
4. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5
5. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |   3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | mirinda       | cola   | tea        |
| Sport      | surfing  | weightlifting | soccer | water-polo |

