.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-12::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, epic, horror, spy
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, golf, lacrosse, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in an even position##4
3. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is golf##5
4. the person watching animation movies is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
5. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching horror movies##5
6. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |  4   |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | horror        | spy        | epic |
| Sport         | lacrosse  | skateboarding | basketball | golf |

