4. the egyptian is somewhere to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
5. the egyptian is on the left of the french##1
6. the person drinking cola is between the person drinking soy-milk and the french##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |       4       |
