.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-19::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, goldfish, hamster, mouse
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, jet-ski, quad-bike, snowmobile
1. the owner of the bird is between the person driving the jet-ski and the owner of the goldfish##2
2. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the right of the owner of the mouse##5
3. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##5
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
5. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Pet         | hamster   | mouse   | bird       | goldfish   |
| Transport   | quad-bike | jet-ski | helicopter | snowmobile |

